  </p>

  <p>
    Outside of work, anime has always been part of life—One Piece, Naruto, manga, all of it.
    I also enjoy meeting people and hearing their stories.
  </p>

  <p>
    Over time, I became more active in communities and met some incredible people,
    including contributors in open-source spaces.
  </p>

